Filename: volumerender_line_profile.py

Line #    Mem usage    Increment  Occurrences   Line Contents
=============================================================
   146    189.0 MiB    189.0 MiB           1   @profile
   147                                         def interpol(i, points, datacube, Nangles):
   148    189.0 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       angle = np.pi/2 * i / Nangles
   149    189.0 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       N = 180
   150    189.0 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       c = np.linspace(-N/2, N/2, N)
   151    322.5 MiB    133.5 MiB           1       qx, qy, qz = np.meshgrid(c, c, c)
   152    322.5 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       qxR = qx
   153    411.7 MiB     89.2 MiB           1       qyR = qy * np.cos(angle) - qz * np.sin(angle) 
   154    456.2 MiB     44.5 MiB           1       qzR = qy * np.sin(angle) + qz * np.cos(angle)
   155    589.7 MiB    133.5 MiB           1       qi = np.array([qxR.ravel(), qyR.ravel(), qzR.ravel()]).T
   156                                             
   157                                             # Interpolate onto Camera Grid
   158    966.7 MiB    377.0 MiB           1       camera_grid = interpn(points, datacube, qi, method='linear').reshape((N, N, N))
   159                                             
   160                                             # Do Volume Rendering
   161    966.7 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       image = np.zeros((camera_grid.shape[1], camera_grid.shape[2], 3))
   162    966.7 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       return image, camera_grid

   123    844.7 MiB    844.7 MiB           1   @profile
   124                                         def transferFunction(x):
   125    845.5 MiB      0.8 MiB           1       r = 1.0*np.exp( -(x - 9.0)**2/1.0 ) +  0.1*np.exp( -(x - 3.0)**2/0.1 ) +  0.1*np.exp( -(x - -3.0)**2/0.5 )
   126    845.5 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       g = 1.0*np.exp( -(x - 9.0)**2/1.0 ) +  1.0*np.exp( -(x - 3.0)**2/0.1 ) +  0.1*np.exp( -(x - -3.0)**2/0.5 )
   127    845.5 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       b = 0.1*np.exp( -(x - 9.0)**2/1.0 ) +  0.1*np.exp( -(x - 3.0)**2/0.1 ) +  1.0*np.exp( -(x - -3.0)**2/0.5 )
   128    845.5 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       a = 0.6*np.exp( -(x - 9.0)**2/1.0 ) +  0.1*np.exp( -(x - 3.0)**2/0.1 ) + 0.01*np.exp( -(x - -3.0)**2/0.5 )
   129    845.5 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       return r, g, b, a

   164    844.4 MiB    844.4 MiB           1   @profile
   165                                         def color_transfer(image, dataslice):
   166    845.5 MiB      1.1 MiB           1       r, g, b, a = transferFunction(np.log(dataslice))
   167    845.5 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       image[:, :, 0] = a * r + (1 - a) * image[:, :, 0]

   170    845.5 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       return image

Line #    Mem usage    Increment  Occurrences   Line Contents
=============================================================
   146    849.9 MiB    849.9 MiB           1   @profile
   147                                         def interpol(i, points, datacube, Nangles):
   148    849.9 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       angle = np.pi/2 * i / Nangles
   149    849.9 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       N = 180
   150    849.9 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       c = np.linspace(-N/2, N/2, N)
   151    850.0 MiB      0.1 MiB           1       qx, qy, qz = np.meshgrid(c, c, c)
   152    850.0 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       qxR = qx
   153    859.5 MiB      9.4 MiB           1       qyR = qy * np.cos(angle) - qz * np.sin(angle) 
   154    859.5 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       qzR = qy * np.sin(angle) + qz * np.cos(angle)
   155    993.0 MiB    133.5 MiB           1       qi = np.array([qxR.ravel(), qyR.ravel(), qzR.ravel()]).T
   156                                             
   157                                             # Interpolate onto Camera Grid
   158   1048.7 MiB     55.8 MiB           1       camera_grid = interpn(points, datacube, qi, method='linear').reshape((N, N, N))
   159                                             
   160                                             # Do Volume Rendering
   161   1048.7 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       image = np.zeros((camera_grid.shape[1], camera_grid.shape[2], 3))
   162   1048.7 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       return image, camera_grid

Line #    Mem usage    Increment  Occurrences   Line Contents
=============================================================
   146    898.6 MiB    898.6 MiB           1   @profile
   147                                         def interpol(i, points, datacube, Nangles):
   148    898.6 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       angle = np.pi/2 * i / Nangles
   149    898.6 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       N = 180
   150    898.6 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       c = np.linspace(-N/2, N/2, N)
   151    898.6 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       qx, qy, qz = np.meshgrid(c, c, c)
   152    898.6 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       qxR = qx
   153    898.6 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       qyR = qy * np.cos(angle) - qz * np.sin(angle) 
   154    898.6 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       qzR = qy * np.sin(angle) + qz * np.cos(angle)
   155   1032.1 MiB    133.5 MiB           1       qi = np.array([qxR.ravel(), qyR.ravel(), qzR.ravel()]).T
   156                                             
   157                                             # Interpolate onto Camera Grid
   158   1037.8 MiB      5.7 MiB           1       camera_grid = interpn(points, datacube, qi, method='linear').reshape((N, N, N))
   159                                             
   160                                             # Do Volume Rendering
   161   1037.8 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       image = np.zeros((camera_grid.shape[1], camera_grid.shape[2], 3))
   162   1037.8 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       return image, camera_grid

Line #    Mem usage    Increment  Occurrences   Line Contents

   146    904.3 MiB    904.3 MiB           1   @profile
   147                                         def interpol(i, points, datacube, Nangles):
   148    904.3 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       angle = np.pi/2 * i / Nangles
   149    904.3 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       N = 180
   150    904.3 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       c = np.linspace(-N/2, N/2, N)
   151    904.3 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       qx, qy, qz = np.meshgrid(c, c, c)
   152    904.3 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       qxR = qx
   153    904.3 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       qyR = qy * np.cos(angle) - qz * np.sin(angle) 
   154    904.3 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       qzR = qy * np.sin(angle) + qz * np.cos(angle)
   155   1037.8 MiB    133.5 MiB           1       qi = np.array([qxR.ravel(), qyR.ravel(), qzR.ravel()]).T
   156                                             
   157                                             # Interpolate onto Camera Grid
   158   1048.9 MiB     11.1 MiB           1       camera_grid = interpn(points, datacube, qi, method='linear').reshape((N, N, N))
   159                                             
   160                                             # Do Volume Rendering
   161   1048.9 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       image = np.zeros((camera_grid.shape[1], camera_grid.shape[2], 3))
   162   1048.9 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       return image, camera_grid

Line #    Mem usage    Increment  Occurrences   Line Contents
=============================================================
   146    915.4 MiB    915.4 MiB           1   @profile
   147                                         def interpol(i, points, datacube, Nangles):
   148    915.4 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       angle = np.pi/2 * i / Nangles
   149    915.4 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       N = 180
   150    915.4 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       c = np.linspace(-N/2, N/2, N)
   151    915.4 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       qx, qy, qz = np.meshgrid(c, c, c)
   152    915.4 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       qxR = qx
   153    915.4 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       qyR = qy * np.cos(angle) - qz * np.sin(angle) 
   154    915.4 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       qzR = qy * np.sin(angle) + qz * np.cos(angle)
   155   1048.9 MiB    133.5 MiB           1       qi = np.array([qxR.ravel(), qyR.ravel(), qzR.ravel()]).T
   156                                             
   157                                             # Interpolate onto Camera Grid
   158   1048.9 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       camera_grid = interpn(points, datacube, qi, method='linear').reshape((N, N, N))
   159                                             
   160                                             # Do Volume Rendering
   161   1048.9 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       image = np.zeros((camera_grid.shape[1], camera_grid.shape[2], 3))
   162   1048.9 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       return image, camera_grid

Line #    Mem usage    Increment  Occurrences   Line Contents
=============================================================
   146    915.4 MiB    915.4 MiB           1   @profile
   147                                         def interpol(i, points, datacube, Nangles):
   148    915.4 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       angle = np.pi/2 * i / Nangles
   149    915.4 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       N = 180
   150    915.4 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       c = np.linspace(-N/2, N/2, N)
   151    915.4 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       qx, qy, qz = np.meshgrid(c, c, c)
   152    915.4 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       qxR = qx
   153    915.4 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       qyR = qy * np.cos(angle) - qz * np.sin(angle) 
   154    915.4 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       qzR = qy * np.sin(angle) + qz * np.cos(angle)
   155   1048.9 MiB    133.5 MiB           1       qi = np.array([qxR.ravel(), qyR.ravel(), qzR.ravel()]).T
   156                                             
   157                                             # Interpolate onto Camera Grid
   158   1060.0 MiB     11.1 MiB           1       camera_grid = interpn(points, datacube, qi, method='linear').reshape((N, N, N))
   159                                             
   160                                             # Do Volume Rendering
   161   1060.0 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       image = np.zeros((camera_grid.shape[1], camera_grid.shape[2], 3))
   162   1060.0 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       return image, camera_grid

Line #    Mem usage    Increment  Occurrences   Line Contents
=============================================================
   146    926.8 MiB    926.8 MiB           1   @profile
   147                                         def interpol(i, points, datacube, Nangles):
   148    926.8 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       angle = np.pi/2 * i / Nangles
   149    926.8 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       N = 180
   150    926.8 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       c = np.linspace(-N/2, N/2, N)
   151    926.8 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       qx, qy, qz = np.meshgrid(c, c, c)
   152    926.8 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       qxR = qx
   153    926.8 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       qyR = qy * np.cos(angle) - qz * np.sin(angle) 
   154    926.8 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       qzR = qy * np.sin(angle) + qz * np.cos(angle)
   155   1060.3 MiB    133.5 MiB           1       qi = np.array([qxR.ravel(), qyR.ravel(), qzR.ravel()]).T
   156                                             
   157                                             # Interpolate onto Camera Grid
   158   1055.6 MiB     -4.7 MiB           1       camera_grid = interpn(points, datacube, qi, method='linear').reshape((N, N, N))
   159                                             
   160                                             # Do Volume Rendering
   161   1055.6 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       image = np.zeros((camera_grid.shape[1], camera_grid.shape[2], 3))
   162   1055.6 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       return image, camera_grid

   126    922.6 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       g = 1.0*np.exp( -(x - 9.0)**2/1.0 ) +  1.0*np.exp( -(x - 3.0)**2/0.1 ) +  0.1*np.exp( -(x - -3.0)**2/0.5 )
   127    922.6 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       b = 0.1*np.exp( -(x - 9.0)**2/1.0 ) +  0.1*np.exp( -(x - 3.0)**2/0.1 ) +  1.0*np.exp( -(x - -3.0)**2/0.5 )

   129    922.8 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       return r, g, b, a

Filename: volumerender_line_profile.py

Line #    Mem usage    Increment  Occurrences   Line Contents
=============================================================
   146    925.5 MiB    925.5 MiB           1   @profile
   147                                         def interpol(i, points, datacube, Nangles):
   148    925.5 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       angle = np.pi/2 * i / Nangles
   149    925.5 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       N = 180
   150    925.5 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       c = np.linspace(-N/2, N/2, N)
   151    925.6 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       qx, qy, qz = np.meshgrid(c, c, c)
   152    925.6 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       qxR = qx
   153    925.7 MiB      0.1 MiB           1       qyR = qy * np.cos(angle) - qz * np.sin(angle) 
   154    925.7 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       qzR = qy * np.sin(angle) + qz * np.cos(angle)
   155   1059.2 MiB    133.5 MiB           1       qi = np.array([qxR.ravel(), qyR.ravel(), qzR.ravel()]).T
   156                                             
   157                                             # Interpolate onto Camera Grid
   158   1059.1 MiB     -0.1 MiB           1       camera_grid = interpn(points, datacube, qi, method='linear').reshape((N, N, N))
   159                                             
   160                                             # Do Volume Rendering
   161   1059.1 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       image = np.zeros((camera_grid.shape[1], camera_grid.shape[2], 3))
   162   1059.1 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       return image, camera_grid


Filename: volumerender_line_profile.py

Line #    Mem usage    Increment  Occurrences   Line Contents
=============================================================
   123    925.6 MiB    925.6 MiB           1   @profile
   124                                         def transferFunction(x):

Filename: volumerender_line_profile.py

Line #    Mem usage    Increment  Occurrences   Line Contents
=============================================================
   146    925.6 MiB    925.6 MiB           1   @profile
   147                                         def interpol(i, points, datacube, Nangles):
   148    925.6 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       angle = np.pi/2 * i / Nangles
   149    925.6 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       N = 180
   150    925.6 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       c = np.linspace(-N/2, N/2, N)
   151    925.6 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       qx, qy, qz = np.meshgrid(c, c, c)
   152    925.6 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       qxR = qx
   153    925.6 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       qyR = qy * np.cos(angle) - qz * np.sin(angle) 
   154    925.6 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       qzR = qy * np.sin(angle) + qz * np.cos(angle)
   155   1059.1 MiB    133.5 MiB           1       qi = np.array([qxR.ravel(), qyR.ravel(), qzR.ravel()]).T
   156                                             
   157                                             # Interpolate onto Camera Grid
   158   1062.5 MiB      3.4 MiB           1       camera_grid = interpn(points, datacube, qi, method='linear').reshape((N, N, N))
   159                                             
   160                                             # Do Volume Rendering
   161   1062.5 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       image = np.zeros((camera_grid.shape[1], camera_grid.shape[2], 3))
   162   1062.5 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       return image, camera_grid

   126    929.0 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       g = 1.0*np.exp( -(x - 9.0)**2/1.0 ) +  1.0*np.exp( -(x - 3.0)**2/0.1 ) +  0.1*np.exp( -(x - -3.0)**2/0.5 )
   127    929.0 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       b = 0.1*np.exp( -(x - 9.0)**2/1.0 ) +  0.1*np.exp( -(x - 3.0)**2/0.1 ) +  1.0*np.exp( -(x - -3.0)**2/0.5 )
   128    929.0 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       a = 0.6*np.exp( -(x - 9.0)**2/1.0 ) +  0.1*np.exp( -(x - 3.0)**2/0.1 ) + 0.01*np.exp( -(x - -3.0)**2/0.5 )

Line #    Mem usage    Increment  Occurrences   Line Contents
=============================================================
   146    929.5 MiB    929.5 MiB           1   @profile
   147                                         def interpol(i, points, datacube, Nangles):
   148    929.5 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       angle = np.pi/2 * i / Nangles
   149    929.5 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       N = 180
   150    929.5 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       c = np.linspace(-N/2, N/2, N)
   151    929.5 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       qx, qy, qz = np.meshgrid(c, c, c)
   152    929.5 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       qxR = qx
   153    929.5 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       qyR = qy * np.cos(angle) - qz * np.sin(angle) 
   154    929.5 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       qzR = qy * np.sin(angle) + qz * np.cos(angle)
   155   1063.0 MiB    133.5 MiB           1       qi = np.array([qxR.ravel(), qyR.ravel(), qzR.ravel()]).T
   156                                             
   157                                             # Interpolate onto Camera Grid
   158   1063.0 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       camera_grid = interpn(points, datacube, qi, method='linear').reshape((N, N, N))
   159                                             
   160                                             # Do Volume Rendering
   161   1063.0 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       image = np.zeros((camera_grid.shape[1], camera_grid.shape[2], 3))
   162   1063.0 MiB      0.0 MiB           1       return image, camera_grid
